{
  "message": "test(fuzz): extend dataframe_merge corpus with 12 edge-case seeds\n\nAdd 12 structured corpus seeds for the dataframe merge fuzz target\ncovering various join type and data distribution edge cases:\n\n- inner_single_each: minimal 1x1 inner join\n- outer_no_overlap: outer join with disjoint keys\n- inner_all_overlap: inner join with full key overlap\n- left_asymmetric: left join 5:1 row ratio\n- right_asymmetric: right join 1:5 row ratio\n- outer_max_rows: outer join at max size (6x6)\n- inner_empty_result: inner join producing empty result\n- left_single_unmatched: left join with unmatched left row\n- right_single_unmatched: right join with unmatched right row\n- outer_partial_overlap: outer join with alternating overlap\n- inner_duplicate_keys: inner join with same keys\n- left_all_matched: left join where all left rows match\n\nAlso adds corresponding fixture tests to fuzz_seed_fixtures.rs.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
